<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TolE0240">
<l>urivaru kālai nāḻik kiḷavi</l>
<l>iṟuti ikara meyyoṭuṅ keṭumē</l>
<l>ṭakara moṟṟu māvayi ṉāṉa</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the word <foreign xml:lang="ta">nāḻi</foreign> ' a corn-measure '</l>
<l>is followed by the word <foreign xml:lang="ta">uri</foreign> ' a corn-measure '</l>
<l>the final <foreign xml:lang="ta">i</foreign> and the consonant are dropped and <foreign xml:lang="ta">ṭ</foreign> takes their place.<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">nāḻi + uri &gt; nāṭuri ; nāḻi </foreign>is the
          eighth part of a marcal ; <foreign xml:lang="ta">uri</foreign> is the sixteenth part of a marcal.</note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
